	<img class="rightFloat" src="../media/LE_AW_017.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"  /><p align="left">The growing popularity of home computers has brought about the biggest single change in the way we spend our free time since the invention of television. This development is viewed by many people as a mixed blessing.</p><p align="left"><font color="#000000">Having a computer at home has undoubted advantages. <select id="q1" type="dropdown" ><option id="o1">Firstly"</option>"<option id="o2">As a result"</option>"<option id="o3">In addition"</option>"<option id="o4">However"</option>"</select>, through the Internet we can make contact with many more people <select id="q2" type="dropdown" ><option id="o5">than"</option>"<option id="o6">who"</option>"<option id="o7">that"</option>"<option id="o8">as"</option>"</select> we would normally meet in our everyday lives: people from other parts of the world and people with similar interests to our own. <select id="q3" type="dropdown" ><option id="o9">Moreover"</option>"<option id="o10">Despite this"</option>"<option id="o11">For instance"</option>"<option id="o12">Therefore"</option>"</select>, it gives us the possibility of sharing information and interests with others more easily than in the past through the use of e-mail and chat programs. <select id="q4" type="dropdown" ><option id="o13">Finally"</option>"<option id="o14">Consequently"</option>"<option id="o15">In contrast"</option>"<option id="o16">To sum up"</option>"</select>, some people believe that computer games are <select id="q5" type="dropdown" ><option id="o17">more stimulating"</option>"<option id="o18">stimulating"</option>"<option id="o19">very stimulating"</option>"<option id="o20">as stimulating"</option>"</select> for our brains than, <select id="q6" type="dropdown" ><option id="o21">for instance"</option>"<option id="o22">such as"</option>"<option id="o23">therefore"</option>"<option id="o24">however"</option>"</select>, watching television because they improve our reactions and our ability to think logically.</font></p><p align="left"><select id="q7" type="dropdown" ><option id="o25">On the other hand"</option>"<option id="o26">What is more"</option>"<option id="o27">In addition"</option>"<option id="o28">Therefore"</option>"</select>, like television, personal computers tend to isolate us from the world just outside our front door. We may speak to friends and neighbours <select id="q8" type="dropdown" ><option id="o29">less"</option>"<option id="o30">more"</option>"<option id="o31">fewer"</option>"<option id="o32">little"</option>"</select> because we are busy playing computer games indoors. <select id="q9" type="dropdown" ><option id="o33">What is more"</option>"<option id="o34">In consequence"</option>"<option id="o35">Lastly"</option>"<option id="o36">As a result of this"</option>"</select>, there is evidence that we are not as <select id="q10" type="dropdown" ><option id="o37">healthy"</option>"<option id="o38">health"</option>"<option id="o39">healthier"</option>"<option id="o40">healthiest"</option>"</select> as we used to be due to the sedentary lifestyle that computers encourage us to lead. Lastly, some psychologists argue that computer games are addictive, which means that some people may be distracted from doing more important things, <select id="q11" type="dropdown" ><option id="o41">such as"</option>"<option id="o42">as"</option>"<option id="o43">whereas"</option>"<option id="o44">as well as"</option>"</select> spending time on their studies or with their family.</p><p align="left"><select id="q12" type="dropdown" ><option id="o45">In conclusion"</option>"<option id="o46">Firstly"</option>"<option id="o47">Consequently"</option>"<option id="o48">Lastly"</option>"</select>, I believe that computers are useful in the home, as long as we use them as a tool, <select id="q13" type="dropdown" ><option id="o49">for example"</option>"<option id="o50">including"</option>"<option id="o51">such as"</option>"<option id="o52">as well as"</option>"</select>, to communicate with friends or find information. <select id="q14" type="dropdown" ><option id="o53">However"</option>"<option id="o54">Although"</option>"<option id="o55">Consequently"</option>"<option id="o56">Moreover"</option>"</select>, they may be harmful when they become our main source of entertainment.</p><p align="left"><font size="2"></font></p>
